Reasoning: 
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is the most likely category as the paper deals with equations and their solvability, which is a topic closely related to logic. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is also likely as the paper discusses vector addition systems and their reachability problem, which are topics related to data structures and algorithms. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is a possible category as the paper deals with the generalization of linear equations to unordered and ordered data vectors, which can be seen as a language-related topic. 
- cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics) is another possible category as the paper deals with the solvability of linear equations, which is a topic related to discrete mathematics. 
- cs.CC (Computational Complexity) is also a possible category as the paper discusses the computational complexity of the solvability problem for linear equations with ordered data vectors.
